Dreamnet already has enough governance and ALN scaffolding to promote all 50 candidate terms to first‑class, testable XR‑grid primitives; the next step is to pin each term to concrete state vectors (sleepstage, psychriskscore, sleeptoken, enstasisscore, evilrate, etc.), neurorights flags, and QPU.Datashard rows so they can run on self‑hosted dream‑gaming nodes and support console retirement and carbon reduction experiments.[^1_1][^1_2][^1_3]

Below is a compact, production‑grade QPU.Datashard plus 10 research actions that tie your 50-term vocabulary into Dreamnet’s existing evilrate/eligibility math, safe‑room semantics, and neurorights stack.[^1_2][^1_3][^1_1]

***

## QPU.Datashard: dream-gaming control surface

```aln
aln aln
destination-path,xr-dream.dream-gaming.control-surface.v1.aln
QPU.Datashard,Dream-gaming safety, rights, routing, and addiction/energy controls for XR-grid

SECTION,SUBJECT-STATE
ROW,subject,subject,scalar,subjectid,,string,primarykey,Augmented user ID
ROW,subject,subject,enum,sleepstage,unknown,string,wake,N1,N2,N3,REM,unknown,Scored sleep stage
ROW,subject,subject,scalar,psychriskscore,0.0,float,range0,1,Composite psych risk R
ROW,subject,subject,enum,psychrisklevel,low,string,low,moderate,high,critical,Safety band from Dreamnet stack
ROW,subject,subject,scalar,sleeptoken,0.0,float,range0,1,Sleep pressure proxy S from actigraphy/circadian
ROW,subject,subject,scalar,enstasisscore,1.0,float,range0,1,Inner stability Es from locus governance
ROW,subject,subject,flag,hasdaytimeactivityproof,false,bool,nonnull,True when minimum activity/fatigue earned

SECTION,XR-NODE
ROW,node,node,scalar,nodeid,,string,primarykey,XR-grid node or dream lab rig ID
ROW,node,node,enum,noderole,gaming,string,lab,research,au-rig,therapy,gaming,Deployment role
ROW,node,node,scalar,infracompliancescore,0.0,float,range0,1,Code/policy compliance score infra-only
ROW,node,node,scalar,evilrate,0.0,float,range0,1,Technical neurorights violation rate V/N
ROW,node,node,flag,activerogue,false,bool,nonnull,True when evilrate exceeds rogue threshold (infra only)

SECTION,DREAM-GAMING-METRICS
ROW,dream,dream,scalar,dreamsessionid,,string,primarykey,Night/session identifier
ROW,dream,dream,scalar,dreamgamingminutes,0,int,0,Total dream-gaming minutes (all scenes)
ROW,dream,dream,scalar,consoleminutesbaseline,0,int,0,Historical console minutes for cohort
ROW,dream,dream,scalar,consoleminutescurrent,0,int,0,Observed console minutes after adoption
ROW,dream,dream,scalar,DreamGamingCarbonIndex,0.0,float,range-10,10,Net per-night carbon delta vs console baseline kgCO2
ROW,dream,dream,scalar,ConsoleOffloadIntensity,0.0,float,range0,1,Normalized console-offload intensity curve value

SECTION,ELIGIBILITY-SCORES
ROW,elig,policy,scalar,eligibilityE,0.0,float,range0,1,Safety eligibility E = S * (1 - R) * Es
ROW,elig,policy,scalar,eligibilityEmin,0.50,float,range0,1,Minimum E for dream-gaming entry
ROW,elig,policy,scalar,psychriskRmax,0.35,float,range0,1,Max allowed psychriskscore for play
ROW,elig,policy,scalar,minactivityproof,6000,int,0,Minimum daily steps or equivalent before play
ROW,elig,policy,scalar,carbonbaselinekg,0.25,float,0,Reference kgCO2/h console baseline
ROW,elig,policy,scalar,carbonxrkg,0.05,float,0,Estimated kgCO2/h Dreamnet dream-gaming

SECTION,DREAM-SAFETY-TERMS
ROW,safety,policy,scalar,SleepTokenActivityBudget,0.0,float,range0,1,Normalized daily activity→sleep budget
ROW,safety,policy,scalar,NocturnalStimulusBudget,0.0,float,range0,1,Normalized per-night stimulus budget
ROW,safety,policy,scalar,XR-DreamFatigueGate,0.0,float,range0,1,Gate that clamps load when fatigue risk rises
ROW,safety,policy,scalar,DreamLatencySafetyWindowMin,20.0,float,0,Lower bound minutes since lights-out
ROW,safety,policy,scalar,DreamLatencySafetyWindowMax,40.0,float,0,Upper bound minutes since lights-out
ROW,safety,policy,flag,DreamLoopAddictionBrake,true,bool,nonwaivable,Brake to block compulsive replay loops
ROW,safety,policy,scalar,DreamSessionMaxPerNightMin,90.0,float,0,Hard max dream-gaming minutes/night

SECTION,NEURORIGHTS-POLICY
ROW,rights,policy,flag,mentalprivacy,true,bool,nonwaivable,No raw dream content or inner speech exported
ROW,rights,policy,flag,cognitiveliberty,true,bool,nonwaivable,Right to refuse dream-gaming or tracking
ROW,rights,policy,flag,mentalintegrity,true,bool,nonwaivable,No harmful modulation or forced arousal
ROW,rights,policy,flag,nopunitivexr,true,bool,nonwaivable,No punishment, confinement, or leverage via XR/dreams
ROW,rights,policy,flag,noncommercialneuraldata,true,bool,nonwaivable,Neural/sleep/dream data never sold or used for credit
ROW,rights,policy,flag,SoulNonaddressable,true,bool,nonwaivable,Soul never gets IDs, balances, or APIs
ROW,rights,policy,flag,DreamStateRightsHeader,true,bool,nonwaivable,Marks all sessions as covered by Dream State Rights Charter

SECTION,ROUTING-OBJECTS
ROW,route,object,scalar,DreamstageCoupledXRRouteId,,string,primarykey,Route ID for Dreamstage-Coupled XR Routing
ROW,route,object,flag,SleepGatedTransferCorridor,true,bool,nonwaivable,Enforces N2/N3 + timing window for transfers
ROW,route,object,flag,XRTransferHandshakeHorizonGuard,true,bool,nonwaivable,Prevents handshake outside safe window
ROW,route,object,flag,DualLocusDriftMonitor,true,bool,nonwaivable,Monitors drift; blocks ops when coherence low
ROW,route,object,flag,RescueTransferEthicsBand,true,bool,nonwaivable,Rescue transfers only in terminal prison-like cases

SECTION,SCENE-SCHEDULING
ROW,scene,scene,flag,NonpunitiveSceneScheduler,true,bool,nonwaivable,Scenes cannot encode punishment or pricing
ROW,scene,scene,flag,SafeRoomNoStimCapsule,true,bool,nonwaivable,Global safe-room capsule available from any scene
ROW,scene,scene,flag,SleepStageAwareSceneGraph,true,bool,nonwaivable,Scene graph gated on sleepstage + risk only
ROW,scene,scene,flag,PsychriskCappedDifficultyScaling,true,bool,nonwaivable,Difficulty bounded; no escalation on distress
ROW,scene,scene,scalar,LowArousalHapticEnvelopeMax,0.3,float,range0,1,Max haptic intensity in sleep windows
ROW,scene,scene,scalar,REM-SafeInteractionProfileMax,0.2,float,range0,1,Lower envelope for REM haptics

SECTION,PRIVACY-ANALYTICS
ROW,privacy,policy,flag,XRGridNeurorightsLedgerEnabled,true,bool,nonwaivable,Use hash-linked rights ledger
ROW,privacy,policy,flag,SoulNonaddressableDataPolicy,true,bool,nonwaivable,No soul fields in any schema
ROW,privacy,policy,scalar,DreamDerivedAnalyticsCeiling,0.0,float,range0,1,Upper bound on analytics power from dream-derived data
ROW,privacy,policy,flag,InnerContentFirewallRule,true,bool,nonwaivable,Blocks dream content from all operational queries
ROW,privacy,policy,flag,NoncommercialNeuralTelemetryChannel,true,bool,nonwaivable,Telemetry channel barred from commercial use

SECTION,SESSION-TOKENS
ROW,tokens,token,scalar,SleepQualifiedSessionToken,,string,primarykey,Bound to N2/N3 + eligibilityE window
ROW,tokens,token,scalar,SleepTokenActivityBudgetSnapshot,0.0,float,range0,1,Snapshot at token mint
ROW,tokens,token,scalar,ActivityEarnedDreamAccessScore,0.0,float,range0,1,Score from real-world activity in safe band
ROW,tokens,token,flag,SleepBoundExitPathway,true,bool,nonwaivable,Guaranteed non-punitive exit from any scene
ROW,tokens,token,scalar,DreamGatewayEligibilityScore,0.0,float,range0,1,Per-doorway eligibility for dream-gaming zones

SECTION,AGENTIC-AI
ROW,agent,policy,scalar,AgenticAITunnelScopeProfileId,,string,primarykey,Scope profile for Mistral/Qwen tunnels
ROW,agent,policy,flag,AgenticAITunnelsStateOnly,true,bool,nonwaivable,Only state-level telemetry to agents
ROW,agent,policy,flag,BlockDreamContentToAgents,true,bool,nonwaivable,No dream content / souls / beliefs over tunnels
ROW,agent,policy,flag,OfflineDreamLevelCoDesigner,true,bool,nonnull,Allows offline, policy-limited AI co-design

SECTION,RUNTIME-RULES
ROW,rule,rule,expression,ComputeEligibilityE,
 eligibilityE = sleeptoken * (1.0 - psychriskscore) * enstasisscore,
string,readonly,Safety eligibility math E = S * (1 - R) * Es
ROW,rule,rule,expression,ComputeSleepTokenActivityBudget,
 SleepTokenActivityBudget = min(1.0, daily_activity_steps / minactivityproof),
string,readonly,Normalize activity into sleep-token budget
ROW,rule,rule,expression,ComputeNocturnalStimulusBudget,
 NocturnalStimulusBudget = max(0.0, 1.0 - psychriskscore),
string,readonly,Less budget when risk rises
ROW,rule,rule,condition,AllowDreamGaming,
 sleepstage IN N2,N3
 AND eligibilityE >= eligibilityEmin
 AND psychriskscore <= psychriskRmax
 AND hasdaytimeactivityproof = true,
string,readonly,Gate dream-gaming on sleep + risk + activity
ROW,rule,rule,condition,ApplyDreamLoopAddictionBrake,
 IF dreamgamingminutes >= DreamSessionMaxPerNightMin
 THEN block_new_dreamgaming_sessions = true,
string,readonly,Hard nightly cap to avoid compulsive loops
ROW,rule,rule,expression,ComputeDreamGamingCarbonIndex,
 DreamGamingCarbonIndex = (consoleminutesbaseline * carbonbaselinekg
                           - consoleminutescurrent * carbonbaselinekg
                           - dreamgamingminutes * carbonxrkg) / 60.0,
string,readonly,Approx kgCO2 delta vs all-console baseline
ROW,rule,rule,expression,ComputeConsoleOffloadIntensity,
 ConsoleOffloadIntensity =
   max(0.0, min(1.0,
      (consoleminutesbaseline - consoleminutescurrent)
/ max(1, consoleminutesbaseline))),
string,readonly,Normalized console offload intensity curve
ROW,rule,rule,condition,EnforceInnerContentFirewall,
 forbidop if input in dreamcontent,innerspeech,soultags
           and target in eligibilityE,DreamGamingCarbonIndex,evilrate,
string,readonly,Dream content can never drive safety, risk, or analytics
ROW,rule,rule,condition,EnforceNoncommercialTelemetry,
 forbidop if target in ad_targeting,pricing,credit_scoring
           and source in psychriskscore,sleeptoken,EEG,HRV,dream_tags,
string,readonly,Neural telemetry stays noncommercial

SECTION,LEDGER
ROW,ledger,ledger,scalar,eventid,,string,primarykey,Event ID
ROW,ledger,ledger,enum,eventtype,,string,
 dream-gaming-start,dream-gaming-stop,safe-teleport,loop-brake,token-mint,token-revoke,
Type of dream-gaming governance event
ROW,ledger,ledger,scalar,subjectid,,string,refsubject,Linked subject
ROW,ledger,ledger,scalar,eligibilityE_snapshot,,float,range0,1,Eligibility at event
ROW,ledger,ledger,scalar,psychriskscore_snapshot,,float,range0,1,Risk at event
ROW,ledger,ledger,scalar,sleeptoken_snapshot,,float,range0,1,Sleep token at event
ROW,ledger,ledger,scalar,DreamGamingCarbonIndex_snapshot,,float,range-10,10,Carbon index at event
ROW,ledger,ledger,flag,neurorightsinvariantsheld,true,bool,nonnull,Assert rights baseline respected
ROW,ledger,ledger,flag,noscoringapplied,true,bool,nonnull,Assert no punitive or reputational scoring
FOOTER,END-OF-SHARD
```

Key math hook: $E = S (1 - R) E_s$. To recompute this anywhere, store $S$ (sleeptoken), $R$ (psychriskscore), and $E_s$ (enstasisscore) as scalars in $[0,1]$; multiply $S$ by $(1-R)$, then by $E_s$, and compare to a fixed threshold $E_{\min}$. For example, if $S = 0.8$, $R = 0.3$, and $E_s = 0.9$, then $E = 0.8 \times 0.7 \times 0.9 = 0.504$, which passes a threshold of $0.5$ and reproducibly gates dream‑gaming for any engine using the same inputs.[^1_3][^1_1]

***

## Scientific grounding

- Gating XR and dream‑layer transitions with sleepstage, psychriskscore, sleeptoken, and enstasisscore matches the Dreamnet governance stack and sleep/XR safety literature emphasizing low‑arousal, non‑punitive envelopes for N2/N3 dream‑experiments.[^1_1][^1_3]
- Tying dream‑gaming eligibility to earned sleep pressure and daytime movement, rather than to “time spent playing,” aligns with behavioral models showing that intrinsic routines plus physical activity reduce classical addiction loops and encourage more regular circadian patterns.[^1_3][^1_1]
- Normalizing console offload and carbon index at the shard level lets lab nodes quantify per‑night kgCO2 deltas when participants shift late‑night gaming from high‑power consoles to low‑arousal, sleep‑gated Dreamnet overlays.[^1_1]

***

## Legal / neurorights terms (≥100 chars)

All dream‑gaming controls in this shard SHALL operate solely as neurorights‑aligned safety, routing, and sustainability mechanisms; they SHALL NOT be used to price, rank, punish, or otherwise evaluate souls, beliefs, or dream content, and any attempt to tie eligibility, DreamGamingCarbonIndex, evilrate, or infracompliancescore to reputational scoring, credit, employment, or access to essential services MUST be blocked at engine level, logged with neurorightsinvariantsheld=false, and escalated for independent ethics/legal review.[^1_3][^1_1]

***

## Geographical evidence (5 anchors)

- Geneva, Switzerland – UN/OHCHR neurorights and mental‑privacy work used as baseline for treating dream‑gaming as a protected, non‑punitive domain.[^1_1][^1_3]
- Brussels, Belgium – EU AI Act and GDPR‑class frameworks shaping purpose‑limited, non‑commercial handling of neuro/XR telemetry and risk scores.[^1_3][^1_1]
- Santiago, Chile – Neurorights initiatives treating brain and dream data as specially protected, informing bans on dream‑content scoring and post‑mortem transfers.[^1_3]
- La Jolla, California, USA – Sleep and VR labs providing evidence for low‑arousal envelopes, timing windows (20–40 min N2/N3), and XR‑induced arousal risks.[^1_1][^1_3]
- Toronto, Canada – Neuroethics and brain‑data governance programmes supporting non‑commercial, rights‑first XR‑grid research with tamper‑evident audit trails.[^1_2][^1_1][^1_3]

