nr.policy,policy,flag,cognitiveLiberty,true,bool,nonwaivable,Refusal of XR/BCI never penalized
nr.policy,policy,flag,mentalIntegrity,true,bool,nonwaivable,No harmful mental modulation
nr.policy,policy,flag,noPunitiveXR,true,bool,nonwaivable,No punitive/coercive content
