sig.module,module,scalar,expectedDigestAlgo,sha1,string,immutable,Digest algorithm
sig.module,module,scalar,expectedDigest,d2897795d7883360b01f054ba42e0d05f1135d31,string,immutable,Expected SHA1 digest
